OL,3,CHolocaust survivors urge Nigel Farage
OL,4,Cto apologise for alleged racist abuse
OL,6,FA group of Holocaust survivors has
OL,7,Fcalled on Nigel Farage to apologise
OL,8,Fover allegations of racism and
OL,9,Fantisemitism during his school days.
OL,11,FThe Reform UK leader has faced claims
OL,12,Fabout his behaviour while he was a
OL,13,Fpupil at Dulwich College, a top
OL,14,Fprivate school in south London.
OL,16,FFarage has denied ever making racist
OL,17,Fremarks in a "malicious or nasty way",
OL,18,Fadding that he could not remember
OL,19,Feverything he said 50 years ago.
