OL,7,Fthat Farage "repeatedly" approached
OL,8,Fhim and said "Hitler was right" while
OL,9,Fthey were pupils at the school.
OL,11,F"Those who hope to lead our country
OL,12,Fshould never divide people by race or
OL,13,Freligion. Antisemitic hatred must
OL,14,Fnever be normalised," the Bafta and
OL,15,FEmmy-winning director and producer
OL,16,Fsaid.
